verbose_text: In OVX mice treated with NNK+ E2 or NNK+ E2+ TCDD, the expression of phospho-IkappaB, nuclear p65, nuclear p50, COX-2, and IkappaB degradation were also significantly increased while the expression of cytoplasmic p65 and p50 were decreased.
evidence: expression of phospho-IkappaB, nuclear p65, nuclear p50
